   By Factor Theorem, p % (factor x) = chop [eval p x]
       root p x
   <=> eval p x = #0                by poly_root_def
   <=> p % (factor x) = chop [#0]   by poly_factor_thm
   <=> p % (factor x) = |0|         by poly_chop_const_zero, poly_chop_const_nonzero
